================================================================================
                        FLEXSPACE SYSTEM FEATURES
                          Complete Feature List
================================================================================

This document lists all features of the FlexSpace platform.

================================================================================
PART 1: WHAT USERS SEE AND USE (Frontend)
================================================================================

1. FINDING A SPACE
   - See coworking spaces on a map (Google Maps)
   - Get driving directions to any space
   - Find spaces near your current location
   - Filter spaces by price, amenities, rating, and location

2. MAKING A BOOKING
   - Book a desk or room in real time
   - See if a space is available instantly
   - Get live updates when availability changes
   - Walk-in booking (no reservation needed)
   - Works on desktop, tablet, or phone (PWA = installs like an app)

3. USER DASHBOARD
   - See your upcoming and past bookings
   - Track loyalty points you've earned
   - View your activity history

4. REVIEWS & RATINGS
   - Rate spaces you've visited
   - Leave written feedback
   - Upload photos with your review

5. LOYALTY POINTS & VOUCHERS
   - Earn points every time you book (₱20 = 1 point)
   - Redeem points for discount vouchers (20 points = ₱1)
   - Use vouchers on future bookings
   - Space owners can create their own promo vouchers
   - Admins can create platform-wide vouchers

6. AI CHAT SUPPORT (Flex Support)
   - Ask questions in Hiligaynon, Tagalog, or English
   - Get space recommendations by district (e.g., "Molo?", "Jaro?")
   - Ask for prices, booking help, or directions
   - Ask who developed the platform or who the team is
   - See when the chatbot is online/offline
   - Messages auto-scroll and support bold text & bullet points
   - Chat can understand follow-up questions

7. USER ACCOUNTS
   - Sign up with email and password
   - Or log in with your Google account
   - Reset password via email OTP (one-time code)
   - Change your password anytime
   - Edit your profile information

8. SPACE OWNER FEATURES
   - Add and manage your own spaces
   - Upload images of your space
   - List amenities (WiFi, parking, etc.)
   - Create staff accounts to help manage bookings
   - Upload GCash or Maya QR codes for payments
   - See real-time occupancy and revenue
   - Track payouts and transaction history
   - Create promo vouchers for your space
   - Assign spaces to districts (Molo, Jaro, etc.)
   - Manage reviews left by users

9. ADMIN FEATURES
   - See platform-wide analytics (users, revenue, top spaces)
   - Approve or reject new space owner applications
   - Approve or block users and space owners
   - Create global vouchers for everyone
   - Turn on maintenance mode
   - Track platform commission earnings
   - View system logs (who did what, when)
   - Monitor the queue system (emails, image uploads)
   - Manage locations and districts
   - Change system settings

10. LANDING PAGE (public, no login required)
    - See featured spaces
    - Learn how FlexSpace works
    - View platform information before signing up

================================================================================
PART 2: SYSTEM BACKGROUND SERVICES (Behind the Scenes)
================================================================================

11. ACTIVITY TRACKING
    - Every user action is automatically recorded
    - Admins can see who did what and when
    - IP addresses are tracked for security
    - Helps resolve disputes and catch problems

12. SECURITY & PROTECTION
    - Passwords are securely encrypted (not stored as plain text)
    - Bot protection on login/register screens
    - Automatic temporary bans for too many requests
    - IP blocking for suspicious activity
    - Different access levels: User, Staff, Space Owner, Admin
    - Automatic attack detection (protection kicks in during traffic spikes)
    - Error tracking (too many errors = temporary ban)

13. REAL-TIME NOTIFICATIONS
    - Live updates without refreshing the page

14. EMAIL NOTIFICATIONS (automatic)
    - Welcome email when you sign up
    - Booking confirmation email
    - Booking completion email (after check out)
    - Password reset email
    - Password reset confirmation email
    - OTP verification email (one-time code)
    - Space approval email (for space owners)
    - Space rejection email (with reason)
    - Voucher redemption email

15. IMAGE UPLOADS
    - Space photos are uploaded to cloud storage
    - Business permits and registration documents are also uploaded here
    - Payment QR codes are stored here

16. QUEUE SYSTEM (keeps things fast)
    - Emails and image uploads happen in the background
    - You don't have to wait for them to finish
    - If something fails, the system tries again up to 3 times
    - If the queue system fails, things still work (just slower)

17. LOCATION FEATURES
    - Spaces are stored with latitude/longitude coordinates
    - The system can find spaces near you
    - Districts help organize spaces by area (Molo, Jaro, etc.)

18. AUTOMATIC BAN SYSTEM
    - Automatic IP blocking after too many violations
    - Temporary bans last 5 minutes by default
    - Permanent bans for repeat offenders
    - Admins can manually block or unblock anyone

19. API VERSIONING
    - The system supports multiple API versions (v1 and v2)
    - Allows new features to be added without breaking old ones

20. MULTI-ENVIRONMENT SUPPORT
    - The system can run in different modes: Local (testing), Staging (preview), Production (live)
    - Each environment has its own settings

================================================================================
PART 3: AI CHATBOT CAPABILITIES (Flex Support)
================================================================================

Flex Support can:

- Detect if you're speaking Hiligaynon, Tagalog, or English automatically
- Greet you in your own language
- List all spaces in a specific district (Molo, Jaro, Mandurriao, etc.)
- Show all spaces grouped by district
- Explain how to book a space (5-step guide)
- Give Google Maps links for any space location
- Tell you the names and roles of all team members
- Tell you who the lead programmer is
- Respond to "help" or "menu" with available options
- Understand and answer follow-up questions

================================================================================
PART 4: SECURITY FEATURES SUMMARY
================================================================================

- JWT tokens (secure session management)
- Bcrypt password hashing (strong encryption)
- Cloudflare Turnstile (bot protection on login/register)
- Rate limiting per IP (300 requests per minute normally, 30 during attacks)
- Request monitoring (800+ total requests per minute triggers strict mode)
- Error tracking (10+ errors = automatic temporary ban)
- IP blocklist with permanent and temporary options
- Role-based access (User, Staff, Space Owner, Admin)
- Auto-logger for audit trails (everything is recorded)

================================================================================
PART 5: TECHNOLOGY STACK (For Reference)
================================================================================

Frontend: React, Vite, Tailwind CSS, Leaflet maps
Backend: Node.js, Express, MongoDB
AI: Google Gemini API
Real-time: Socket.io
Security: JWT, Bcrypt, Cloudflare Turnstile
Queue: Bull, Redis
Storage: Cloudinary (images), MongoDB (data)
Email: Nodemailer, Gmail SMTP
Container: Docker
Deployment: Vercel (frontend), Render (backend)

